1.1.name: wordpress/extended-user-profile
1.1.description:
The webmaster can extended with the basic html knowledge, or even with some copy paste skills to add more input fields or textareas to their user profile form.

PAY ATTENTION IT WILL NOT WORK WITH OLDER PLUGIN VERSIONS VERSION SO YOU MIGHT NEED TO CHANGE YOUR TEMPLATE
